Package: astho.viz
Title: Create Data Visualization in Highcharts using ASTHO Themes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lindsay", "Jorgenson", , "ljorgenson@astho.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Build accessible {highcharter} visualizations themed for the 
    Association of State and Territorial Health Officials (ASTHO). 
   This packages currently can be used to create maps (with or without 
   U.S. Territories and Freely Associated States), pie charts and bar graphs 
   (cluster, drill, grouped, and regular).
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
URL: https://github.com/lindsayjorgenson/astho.viz
BugReports: https://github.com/lindsayjorgenson/astho.viz/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    custom.map,
    dplyr,
    highcharter,
    magrittr
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
